Class AbstractEntity

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.BombingGames.WurfelEngine.Core.Gameobjects.AbstractGameObject
      • com.BombingGames.WurfelEngine.Core.Gameobjects.AbstractEntity
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    HasID, java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Bullet, EntityShadow, Explosion, MovableEntity, Selection, SimpleEntity

    public abstract class AbstractEntity
extends AbstractGameObject
    An entity is a game object wich is self aware that means it knows it's position.
